originalSql:
SELECT 
    p.p_brand,
    COUNT(DISTINCT p.p_partkey) AS unique_parts,
    SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS total_avail_qty,
    AVG(p.p_retailprice) AS avg_retail_price,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT s.s_name, ', ') AS suppliers,
    CONCAT('Region: ', r.r_name, ' (', COUNT(DISTINCT n.n_nationkey), ' Nations)') AS region_info
FROM 
    part p
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey
JOIN 
    supplier s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN 
    nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN 
    region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
WHERE 
    p.p_retailprice > 50.00
    AND s.s_acctbal > 1000.00
GROUP BY 
    p.p_brand, r.r_name
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.s_suppkey) > 2
ORDER BY 
    total_avail_qty DESC, avg_retail_price ASC

SELECT COALESCE("t5"."P_BRAND", "t5"."P_BRAND") AS "P_BRAND", "t5"."UNIQUE_PARTS", "t5"."TOTAL_AVAIL_QTY", "t5"."AVG_RETAIL_PRICE", "t5"."SUPPLIERS", CONCAT('Region: ', "t5"."r_name", ' (', CAST("t5"."FD_D_f6" AS VARCHAR), ' Nations)') AS "REGION_INFO"
FROM (SELECT "t1"."p_brand" AS "P_BRAND", "region"."r_name", COUNT(DISTINCT "t1"."p_partkey") AS "UNIQUE_PARTS", SUM("s1"."ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_AVAIL_QTY", AVG("t1"."p_retailprice") AS "AVG_RETAIL_PRICE", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "t0"."s_name", ', ') AS "SUPPLIERS", COUNT(DISTINCT "nation"."n_nationkey") AS "FD_D_f6", COUNT(DISTINCT "t0"."s_suppkey") AS "FD_D_f7"
FROM "region"
INNER JOIN "nation" ON "region"."r_regionkey" = "nation"."n_regionkey"
INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM "supplier"
WHERE "s_acctbal" > 1000.00) AS "t0" ON "nation"."n_nationkey" = "t0"."s_nationkey"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "part"
WHERE "p_retailprice" > 50.00) AS "t1" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "t1"."p_partkey" = "s1"."ps_partkey") ON "t0"."s_suppkey" = "s1"."ps_suppkey"
GROUP BY "t1"."p_brand", "region"."r_name"
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT "t0"."s_suppkey") > 2
ORDER BY 4 DESC NULLS FIRST, 5) AS "t5"
